title: Would you like to add a BabyQuick Farm?
body:
Hello KOGE hodlers and those that like to govern.  You love DEFI and Crypto and we do too at BabyQuick!  We would like to offer and add a FARM on the KOGEFARM.io where you can stake KOGE coins and be rewarded in BABYQUICK tokens!   BabyQuick is one of the newest Polygon-based communities that are rewarding holders with QUICK tokens every day!

QUICK Exchange has become one of the top contenders in the DEX space and the liquidity pairs with QUICK token are growing rapidly.  BABYQUICK has unique capabilities to "auto yield" into your public wallet address where you hold BABYQUICK and the BABYQUICK DIV token.   There is no second site address to remember, no added gas fees to harvest, you just hold it in your wallet and with the magic of smart contracts, the token is "auto-staked" and rewards you with QUICK based on our volume and liquidity pair on the exchange.  https://babyquick.app/

This space is all about bringing more projects together and is what makes this community so special.   Staking KOGE coins gives even more utility as additional projects are farmed with the KOGE coin.  This is similar to what you see on other BSC sites like Pancake Swap or Polygon sites like PolyCrystal.  That is one of our missions in the space to expose newcomers and veterans alike to multiple projects that grow symbiotically with time and are within the Polygon community! The BABYQUICK community currently offers a faucet of Matic and BabyQuick to get brand new folks started on Matic Main Net.  NFT contests, giveaways, promotions are just a few of the events that are going on while we continue to expand and partner within the space.

0x9a05D1FF699ea187Dc8523E333eD63503f0d82db  is the contract for those looking to find more info or https://t.me/babyquick to meet the community and see what we have been up to!  (TASTY SHEEP)

Currently, only the KOGE supply pool and KogeCoin-Matic LP are farm options.  This would be the first project FARM on KogeFarm.io/farms you can earn another crypto by staking KOGE!

Would you like to add a BabyQuick Farm for staking KOGE to the FARM options?
choices: No, I only want a KOGE farm.
